          "publicReply": "=Hi {{ $(\"Zendesk Ticket Trigger\").item.json.ticket.requester.name }},\n\nWe looked into your order and it is currently being packed by our fulfillment team.\n\nWe will send you a tracking link the moment it leaves our facility!\n\nBest,",
